description: McKay-Thompson series of class 10D for the Monster group.

Index entries for McKay-Thompson series for Monster simple group
formula: G.f. is Fourier series of a weight 0 level 10 modular form. f(-1/ ( 10 t)) = f(t) where q = exp(2 pi i t).
